memberships database documentation

memberships.Rd

memberships database documentation

Usage

memberships

Format

The memberships database is a list that contains the following 2 datasets: GPTAD_MEM, DESTA_MEM. For more information and references to each of the datasets used, please use the data_source() and data_contrast() functions.

GPTAD_MEM:

A dataset with 2201 observations and the following 9 variables: manyID, CountryID, Title, Beg, Signature, Force, CountryName, gptadID, treatyID.

DESTA_MEM:

A dataset with 7492 observations and the following 9 variables: manyID, CountryID, Title, Beg, Signature, Force, CountryName, destaID, treatyID.
